high_descs: Pick up the fork to the left of the glass on the countertop that is to the left of the stove.
Place the fork in the glass, handle end down.
Pick up the glass with the fork in it.
Turn around and carry the glass to the sink.
Place the glass with the fork in it into the sink to the right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Move a glass and fork from the countertop to the sink

high_descs: Walk forward to the stove top.
Pick up the fork on the counter to the left of the stove top.
Put the fork inside the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the cup into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it inside a sink basin.

high_descs: Go straight back to the stove across the kitchen.
Pick up the fork from the counter to the right of the stove.
Stand the fork up in the glass on the counter.
Pick up the glass and fork from the counter.
Hold the glass and turn around and find the sink on the left side.
Place the glass and fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a glass and fork to the sink.
